ndamentals, the book also includes the associated body of rules and regulations as well as examples of how they are embodied in actual projects and perspectives on their development in the larger European context.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Mai 2021) 4aBarrierefreiheit. 4aBauen für alle. 4aIntegrale Planung. 4aUniversal Design. 7aARCHITECTURE / General.2bisacsh1 aDegenhart, Christine, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aEbe, Johann, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut0 cprintz978303460577940uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783034615723423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783034615723.jpg  aGBV-deGruyter-alles